      <Value><![CDATA[Learning With Little Jack]]></Value>
    </newsTitle>
    <newsExcerpt>
      <Value><![CDATA[Join Little Jack as he leads kids through curiosity-driven adventures across Cow Paradise Island.]]></Value>
    </newsExcerpt>
    <newsBody>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Little Jack is the heart of our Moo Family community. Every adventure he leads is designed to spark curiosity and build confidence in young learners.</p><p>From spelling and numbers to teamwork and kindness, his stories cover the building blocks of childhood growth.</p>]]></Value>
